{"tid":2058788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱欣就並非妥為當選上訴 並稱上訴判決前仍然是立法會議員","createTime":"2020-06-10T12:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T15:55:15.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7eaf2a997871d9335964929351660f7fc06f365f","tid":2058788,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"工黨劉小麗於2018年立法會九龍西補選中被取消參選資格，她提出選舉呈請，上月獲裁定勝訴，法庭指於補選中勝出的陳凱欣並非妥為當選。陳凱欣今日指，在聽取團隊和法律意見後，已向終審法院提出上訴。她強調，直到法院作出最終判決之前，她仍會繼續「做好立法會議員身份」，並會欣然接受任何結果。<br />\n<br />\n陳凱欣形容上月底法庭的裁決為「小小挫折」，為她帶來不少困難，但卻提醒了她，「我係透過公平、公開、公正嘅選舉而選出嘅民選議員，有超過十萬零六千人嘅信任」，自覺要據理力爭，遂向法庭提出上訴。她表示，自己和團隊已經「盡晒力」，希望最終能夠有公平的判決。她又指「之前嘅裁決其實都係選舉主任出現問題」，強調自己「一直有依足程序。」陳凱欣又指自己「繼續係嗰個陳凱欣」，將繼續努力履行議員責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074380&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVayJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=a30a1f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074380&h=acb8345b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074380</a>"},{"pid":"8065238da3b4586520fd8466bf822a8ce94b68d9","tid":2058788,"uid":180814,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae81d80f94b94628031906cc4b253fe22917bf5","tid":2058788,"uid":62670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/054A7NA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F054A7NA.png&h=e002eebd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7cc0e4e808e72ba17d526e0eb2ca9fd3224211a","tid":2058788,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"還返D糧先啦"},{"pid":"a6ea197b101653717df658f33a4398bc25fc2ee9","tid":20